      "title": "Hungry Eyes",
      "score": 0.07467171848087374,
      "text": "Hungry Eyes\n``Hungry Eyes ''is a song performed by American artist Eric Carmen, a former member of the band Raspberries, and was featured in the film Dirty Dancing. The song was recorded at Beachwood Studios in Beachwood, Ohio in 1987.`` Hungry Eyes'' peaked at # 4 on the Billboard Hot 100 chart and # 3 on the Cash Box Top 100 in 1988. The power ballad was not released commercially in the UK, but it managed to peak at # 82 in January 1988, having charted purely on import sales.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.0510040395964147,
        "graph": 0.051964659230928086,
        "fact": 0.20686732622378154
      }
    },
