      "title": "Cleveland, North Carolina",
      "score": 0.07178376094800848,
      "text": "Cleveland, North Carolina\nCleveland is a town in the Cleveland Township of Rowan County, North Carolina, United States. The population was 871 at the 2010 census.",
      "score_breakdown": {
        "dense": 0.049992368223829346,
        "graph": 0.048638745131100745,
